Chargers Defensive Tackle Garay Is Fined $15,000 for Brady Hit, ESPN Says

-- B y   J a y   B e b e r m a n
-- 
2011-09-22T18:32:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-22/chargers-defensive-tackle-garay-is-fined-15-000-for-brady-hit-espn-says.html
San Diego Chargers defensive tackle
Antonio Garay has been fined $15,000 for hitting New England
Patriots quarterback  Tom Brady  below the knee in a game on Sept.
18, ESPN reported, citing a person familiar with the situation.  The Patriots beat the Chargers 35-21.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jay Beberman at 
 jbeberman@bloomberg.net  